divs: Sighting Detailsi see these orbs every night at work and they seem to be hovering and even changing there position ulmost in sink.one of these things will change its position and very shortly the others will move so they keep there initial pattern and the srangest part is they dont seem to follow the normal shift of stars as the planet rotates it seems to be moving very slowly mind you in the oppisite direction.also as i watched these whatever you want to call them i seen somthing shoot across there veiw .this thing was moving so fast it looked like a flash of ulmost tranparent light but it had a shape to the front of it like it were pointed the rest of it was blurred do to the ungodley speed it was traveling.im not the only one who has seen these oddities but im the only one who will admit it ive watched alot of strange thing go on in that area of the sky for months now and im beginning to wonder if alot of what we think are stars arent.
